# Screenshots Directory

This directory contains application screenshots for documentation purposes.

## Naming Convention
- `v{version}-{description}.png`
- Example: `v0.1.3-main-interface.png`

## Screenshot Guidelines
- Capture at standard desktop resolution (1920x1080 recommended)
- Show key features and functionality
- Include version number in interface when possible
- Use consistent browser window size for comparable views

